Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl
    7     | TypedefDecl

    8 TypedefDecl: TYPEDEF VarType IDENTIFIER SEMICOLON

    9 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
   10         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

   11 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   12 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   13 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   14 VarType: _VarType
   15        | CONST _VarType

   16 _VarType: BuiltinType
   17         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   18         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   19         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   20         | _VarType ASTERISK
   21         | IDENTIFIER

   22 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   23        | VarInit
   24        | ε

   25 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   26        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr
   27        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE InitList RBRACE
   28        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN LBRACE RBRACE

   29 InitList: InitList COMMA InitItem
   30         | InitItem

   31 InitItem: Expr
   32         | LBRACE InitList RBRACE

   33 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   34               | ArrayBound
   35               | ε

   36 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET
   37           | LBRACKET RBRACKET

   38 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   39          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   40          | Param
   41          | ELLIPSES
   42          | ε

   43 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   44      | VarType

   45 BuiltinType: CHAR
   46            | SHORT
   47            | INT
   48            | LONG
   49            | UNSIGNED
   50            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   51            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   52            | UNSIGNED INT
   53            | UNSIGNED LONG
   54            | FLOAT
   55            | DOUBLE
   56            | BOOL
   57            | VOID

   58 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   59           | ε

   60 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   61          | SEMICOLON

   62 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   63           | IDENTIFIER
   64           | ε

   65 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   66         | Enum
   67         | ε

   68 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   69     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   70 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   71      | ε

   72 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   73     | IfStmt
   74     | SwitchStmt
   75     | ForStmt
   76     | DoStmt
   77     | WhileStmt
   78     | ContinueStmt
   79     | BreakStmt
   80     | ReturnStmt
   81     | Block
   82     | TypeDecl
   83     | VarDecl
   84     | SEMICOLON

   85 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   86       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   87 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   88 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   89             | ε

   90 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   91         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   92 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   93        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   94        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   95 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   96 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   97 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   98 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   99 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
  100           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

  101 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

  102 Expr: IDENTIFIER
  103     | Constant
  104     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  105     | Expr COMMA Expr
  106     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
